Arthur O. ARMSTRONG, Petitioner
v.
NORTH CAROLINA, et al.
No. 19-5886
Supreme Court of the United States.
November 12, 2019
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petitions for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
